>\n<h3>影片截图：</h3>\n<p><img class=\\\\\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-12340\\\\\" alt=\\\\\"伤心童话\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/01/jmk4vw4uv2c.jpg\\\\\" alt=\\\\\"[伤心童话][HD-MKV/4.4G][720P][高清电影][中英字幕]\\\\\" width=\\\\\"620\\\\\" height=\\\\\"349\\\\\" /><br />\n<img class=\\\\\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-12341\\\\\" alt=\\\\\"伤心童话\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/01/1b3cjw0g5e3.jpg\\\\\" alt=\\\\\"[伤心童话][HD-MKV/4.4G][720P][高清电影][中英字幕]\\\\\" width=\\\\\"620\\\\\" height=\\\\\"349\\\\\" /></p>\n<div class=\\\\\"dw-box dw-box-download\\\\\"><i class=\\\\\"dwicon-download\\\\\"></i>\n<a href=\\\\\"/01/xlyxxmma1ct.torrent\\\\\">Sad_Fairy_Tale</a></div>\n');");
